trans-unit.source: Implements a selectable item in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.TreeView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer valgbar element i en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.TreeView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: TreeViewItem is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedItemsControl>, which means its header and collection of objects can be of any type (such as string, image, or panel).
trans-unit.target: TreeViewItem er en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedItemsControl>, noe som betyr topp- og objektsamlingen kan være av en annen type (for eksempel streng, image eller panelet).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedItemsControl> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedItemsControl>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedItemsControl>

trans-unit.source: TreeViewItem controls can be embedded inside other TreeViewItem controls to create a hierarchy of nodes inside a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView> control.
trans-unit.target: TreeViewItem kontroller kan bygges inn i andre TreeViewItem Kontroller å opprette et hierarki med noder i en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>

trans-unit.source: The following illustration shows a hierarchy of TreeViewItem controls inside a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>.
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser et hierarki med TreeViewItem kontroller i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>

trans-unit.source: ![TreeView illustration](~/add/media/treeviewillustration.JPG "TreeView illustration") To expand or collapse a TreeViewItem, use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem.IsExpanded%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: ![TreeView illustrasjonen](~/add/media/treeviewillustration.JPG "TreeView illustrasjonen") for å vise eller skjule en TreeViewItem, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem.IsExpanded%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem.IsExpanded%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView> control, see the [TreeView Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>styre, kan du se den [TreeView oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView>

trans-unit.source: Customizing the TreeViewItem Control To apply the same property settings to multiple TreeViewItem controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Tilpasse den TreeViewItem kontrollen til gjelder samme egenskapsinnstillingene flere TreeViewItem kontroller, bruk av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can modify the default <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> to give the control a unique appearance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan endre standard <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>Gi kontrollen unikt utseende.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: For more information about creating a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, see [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om hvordan du oppretter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, se [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: To see the parts and states that are specific to the TreeViewItem, see [TreeView Styles and Templates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se delene og statusene som er spesifikke for TreeViewItem, kan du se [TreeView stiler og maler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Dependency properties for this control might be set by the control’s default style.

trans-unit.source: The default style is determined by which desktop theme is used when the application is running.
